! The playset comes with four diecast cars and with no assembly required, this dinosaur toys transport truck is ready to go right out of the box</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">AWESOME CAR LAUNCH ACTION: This epic T Rex diecast car transport truck features a fierce dinosaur design and an exciting launch action, that sends diecast cars flying into adventure!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SUPER COOL CAR SLIDE: What’s more, the top of the dinosaur truck transporter lifts open to create a 15 inch long slide; Simply push the legs down and lock into place for another exciting way for kids and toddlers to play!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">TACTILE TOYS FOR BOYS: Let their imaginations roar with this hands on dinosaur toys diecast cars playset! Kids will love creating lots of fun pretend play scenarios, while it also encourages eye hand coordination and dexterity, as well as hands on and screen free playtime with friends and family</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE AND SAFE: Built to withstand even the most thrilling prehistoric adventures, this dinosaur themed truck transporters are safe and durable enough for all kinds of active playtime and is easy to wipe down; designed with little hands in mind, this playset is suitable for children ages three and up</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Kidplokio 3 in 1 Ultimate T Rex Diecast Cars Transporter Truck Toy (2 Colors)</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">39.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Roaring fun meets high speed action with Kidplokio’s Ultimate T Rex Diecast Cars Transport Truck! This dinosaur toys diecast car transport truck features a fierce dinosaur design, an exciting car launch action, 15 inch long car slide and four brightly colored diecast cars to play with. This fierce T Rex transport truck is designed for dino lovers and budding racers alike, making it the ultimate transport truck and display case for diecast cars!\n\nLAUNCH ACTION: This epic T Rex diecast car transport truck features an exciting launch action, that sends diecast cars flying into adventure\n\nCAR SLIDE: Open the top of the transporter truck to create a 15 inch long slide, simply push the legs down and lock into place for another exciting way for kids and toddlers to play\n\nDINO DISPLAY CASE: When not in use, the T Rex transport truck keeps diecast cars neatly tucked away and organized until playtime can begin again\n\nThis dinosaur truck playset also encourages engaging playtime sessions where kids imaginations can roar! Toddlers and little ones will love creating fun pretend play scenarios, while also encouraging eye hand coordination and dexterity, as well as hands on and screen free playtime with friends and family. And, with a built in carry handle and snap close side doors, kids can easily tote this T Rex truck transporter to go for playdates, travel and more.\n\nPerfect for both playtime and display, this truck is a must have for every little dinosaur lover. Buckle up for thrilling adventures, where the roar of excitement never ends!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?